it.dc.bridge.om

Class Options

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.dc.bridge.om.Options

  • public class Options
extends java.lang.Object
    The Options class is a collection of CoAP option fields. Both requests and responses may include a list of one or more options. This class contains only the options used in the AllJoyn network.
